OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with outbreaks of rain,
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy at first. Some
OL,9,Fdrier and clearer spells may develop
OL,10,Fat times overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FAny cloud and rain at first
OL,13,Fwill gradually clear to bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells in the morning. Bright
OL,15,Fspells and a few showers developing in
OL,16,Fthe afternoon, heavy at times.
